==保护现状==
绒毛丝鼠属于[[濒危物种|濒危物种]]，在智利哺乳动物中有着第二高的优先保护权。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Cofré | first1 = H. | last2=Marquet| first2=P.A.| title = Conservation status, rarity, and geographic priorities for conservation of Chilean mammals: an assessment| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_biological-conservation_1999-04_88_1/page/53 | journal = Biological Conservation | volume = 88| pages = 53–68 | year = 1999 | doi = 10.1016/S0006-3207(98)00090-1}}</ref>

